Dump zarr like ncdump

Source: R/dump.R
zdump.Rd

Prints an ncdump-like output to the console.

Usage

zdump(store)

Arguments

store

path to store, open zarr store, or open zarr group

Value

a list of lines printed to the console invisibly

Examples

store <- rnz::z_demo()

zdump(store)
